00:00:00,445 --> 00:00:02,835
I spent the next day preparing the boat.
第二天我便着手整备船只

2
00:00:03,645 --> 00:00:05,705
I filled my stores with fresh water,
我储备了清水

3
00:00:05,825 --> 00:00:08,525
ate sea weed until my stomach could take no more,
用海藻拼命把肚子填满

4
00:00:08,605 --> 00:00:11,325
and brought as many meerkats as I could fit into
为了解决理查德·帕克的果腹问题

5
00:00:11,325 --> 00:00:13,345
the storey's locker for Richard Parker.
还把储物柜里塞满了海岛猫鼬

6
00:00:15,405 --> 00:00:17,505
I couldn't leave without him, of course.
我当然不能把他丢下

7
00:00:17,505 --> 00:00:19,375
It would be killing him.
他会死在这儿的

8
00:00:21,275 --> 00:00:25,985
And so I waited for his return.
所以我等他归来

9
00:00:26,325 --> 00:00:28,255
I knew he wouldn't be late.
我知道他不会迟到

